During the bug hunt in https://github.com/ergoplatform/ergo/issues/1627 I found and fixed the following:
- missing check in our BIP32 secret key derivation;
- less than 32 bit bigint import fail in `DlogProverInput::from_biguint`;

Also added test vectors from ergo-wallet incorrect BIP32 secret derivation and appkit test vectors.

Ref #481

This PR partially drafts p2p networking layer. 
Missing parts (to be implemented later):
